<div class="text-center">
    <h2 class="display-5">Introduction to DevOps</h2>
    <p>DevOps is a set of practices that combines software development (Dev) and IT operations (Ops). It aims to shorten the systems development life cycle and provide continuous delivery with high software quality. <a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/devops">Learn more about DevOps.</a></p>
