<div class="text-center">
    <h2 class="display-5">DevOps Tools and Technologies</h2>
    <p>DevOps involves a variety of tools and technologies that help automate and streamline processes. Some popular DevOps tools include:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Git and GitHub for version control</li>
        <li>Jenkins for continuous integration and continuous delivery (CI/CD)</li>
        <li>Docker for containerization</li>
        <li>Kubernetes for container orchestration</li>
        <li>Terraform for infrastructure as code</li>
    </ul>
